      <title>Test</title>
      <link href="/blog/Test/"/>
      <url>/blog/Test/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Ramanujan和"><a href="#Ramanujan和" class="headerlink" title="Ramanujan和"></a>Ramanujan和</h1><p>对数论函数$f,g$考虑和式</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S_{f,g}(n;k)=\sum_{d\mid (n,k)}f(d)g(k/d)</script><blockquote><p><strong>命题</strong><br>$S(n;k)$是积性函数，即对</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">(n_1,n_2)=(k_1,k_2)=(n_1,k_2)=(n_2,k_1)=1</script><p>有</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(n_1n_2;k_1k_2)=S(n_1;k_1)S(n_2;k_2)</script></blockquote><p><em>Proof:</em><br>记$a_1=(n_1,k_1)$,$a_2=(n_2,k_2)$,则</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(n_1n_2;k_1k_2)=\sum_{d\mid a_1a_2} f(d)g(k_1k_2/d)</script><p>注意到$a_1$和$a_2$也互质,故上式可以写成</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{d\mid a_1a_2}f(d)g(k_1k_2/d)=\sum_{d_1\mid a_1}f(d_1)g(k_1/d_1)\sum_{d_2  \mid a_{2}} f\left(d_{2}\right) h\left(k_{2} / d_{2}\right)</script><p>证毕！</p><blockquote><p><strong>命题</strong><br>设$f$是完全积性函数,$g$是积性函数,满足对任意素数$p$有</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(p)\neq0,f(p)\neq g(p)</script><p>设</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">h(n)=\mu(n)g(n),F(n)=f*h</script><p>则</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(n;k)=h\left(\frac{k}{(n,k)}\right)F(k)/F\left(\frac{k}{(n,k)}\right)</script></blockquote><p><em>Proof:</em><br>记</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">R(n;k)=h\left(\frac{k}{(n,k)}\right)F(k)/F\left(\frac{k}{(n,k)}\right)</script><p>明显的看出$R$是积性($F$,$h$都是积性)，那么只需对任意素数$p$证明</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">R(p^a;p^b)=S(p^a;p^b)\qquad(a,b\in\mathbb{N})</script><p>令$c=\min(a,b)$,则</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(p^a;p^b)=\sum_{r=0}^{c}f\left(p^r\right)\mu\left(p^{b-r}\right) g\left(p^{b-r}\right)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">R(p^a;p^b)=\mu\left(p^{b-c}\right)g\left(p^{b-c}\right)F\left(p^b\right)/F\left(p^{b-c}\right)</script><p>我们分三种情况考虑(1)$b-c\ge2$;(2)$b=c$;(3)$b-c=1$.情况(1)是喜闻乐见的消消乐，容易证明上面两式相等;情况(2)</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(p^a;p^b)=\sum_{r=0}^{b}f\left(p^r\right) g\left(p^{b-r}\right)\mu\left(p^{b-r}\right)=F\left(p^b\right)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">R(p^a;p^b)=\mu(1)g(1)F\left(p^b\right)/F(1)=F\left(p^b\right)</script><p>情况(3)</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(p^a;p^b)=\sum_{r=0}^{b-1}f\left(p^r\right)\mu\left(p^{b-r}\right)g\left(p^{b-r}\right)=f(p^{b-1})\mu(p)g(p)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">R(p^a;p^b)=\mu(p)g(p)F(p^b)/F(p)</script><p>而</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">F\left(p^b\right)=\sum_{d\mid p^b}f(d)\mu\left(p^b/d\right)g\left(p^b/d\right)=f\left(p^b\right)-f\left(p^{b-1}\right) g(p)=f\left(p^{b-1}\right)(f(p)-g(p))</script><p>因此$F(p^b)/F(P)=f(p^{b-1})$,即$S(p^a;p^b)=R(p^a;p^b)$.</p><blockquote><p><strong>注</strong>由辗转相除法注意到$(n+k,k)=(n,k)$,所以$S(n;k)$对$n$是以$k$为周期的周期函数.</p></blockquote><p>我们知道,对任意两个长度为$k$的复数列$(z_k)$和$(\omega_k)$,存在唯一的多项式</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">P(x)=\zeta_{0}+\zeta_{1} x+\cdots+\zeta_{k-1} x^{k-1}</script><p>满足$P(\omega_i)=z_i(i=0,1,\cdots,k-1)$,即</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">z_{r}=\zeta_{0}+\zeta_{1} \omega_{r}+\zeta_{2} \omega_{r}^{2}+\cdots+\zeta_{k-1} \omega_{r}^{k-1} \quad(r=0,1,\cdots, k-1</script><p>为了迎合下文,我们只打算取$\omega_{r}=e^{2\pi ir/k}(r=0,1,\cdots,k-1)$.</p><blockquote><p><strong>定义</strong><br>称形如($c(m)$是以$k$为周期的数论函数)</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{m\bmod k}c(m)e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)</script><p>为<em>有限Fourier级数</em>.</p><p><strong>定理</strong><br>对每个周期为$k$的数论函数$f$,对应唯一一个周期为$k$的数论函数$g$,满足</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(n)=\sum_{m\bmod k}g(m)e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)</script><p>实际上, $g$可以被确定为</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">g(n)=\frac1k\sum_{m\bmod k}f(m)e\left(-\frac{mn}{k}\right)</script><hr><p><strong>命题</strong><br>$S(n;k)$的有限Fourier级数为</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S(n;k)=\sum_{m\bmod k}a_k(m)e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)</script><p>其中,</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">a_k(m)=\frac1k\sum_{d\mid(m,n)}dh(d)f(k/d)</script></blockquote><p><em>Proof:</em></p><p>考虑</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{m=1}^{k} a_{k}(m) e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\frac1k\sum_{m=1}^{k} \sum_{d\mid m,d\mid k}dh(d)f(k/d)e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)</script><p>记$m=cd$,则上式变为</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{d\mid k}h(d)\frac{f(k/d)}{(k/d)}\sum_{c=1}^{k/d}e\left(\frac{mc}{k/d}\right)</script><p>注意到第二个和式的值为$k/d$或$0$(取决于$k/d$是否整除$n$),故</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{m=1}^{k} a_{k}(m) e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\sum_{d\mid k,k/d\mid n}h(d)f(k/d)=\sum_{d\mid(n, k)}f(d)h(k/d)=S(n;k)</script><blockquote><p><strong>推论</strong></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{m\bmod k}(m,k)e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\sum_{d\mid(n, k)}d\varphi(k/d)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">k \sum_{m\bmod k} \frac{\varphi((m, k))}{(m,k)}e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\sum_{d\mid(n,k)}d^{2}\mu(k/d)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{m\bmod k} \frac{(m,k)}{\varphi((m,k))}e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\sum_{d\mid(n,k)}d\frac{\mu^2(k/d)}{\varphi(k/d)}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{m \bmod k} \log (m, k)e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\sum_{d\mid(n,k)} d\Lambda(k/d)</script></blockquote><hr><blockquote><p><strong>定义</strong><br>定义<em>Ramanujan和</em> $c_k(n)$为</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">c_k(n)=\sum_{\substack{m\bmod k\\(m, k)=1}}e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)</script><p><strong>命题</strong><br>     (1)</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">     c_k(n)=\sum_{\substack{m\bmod k\\(m, k)=1}}e\left(\frac{mn}{k}\right)=\sum_{d\mid(n,k)}d\mu(k/d)</script><p>(2)</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">c_k(n)=\frac{\mu\left(\frac{k}{(n,k)}\right) \varphi(k)}{\varphi\left(\frac{k}{(n, k)}\right)}</script><hr><p><em>Proof:</em><br>     取$f(n)=n$,$h(n)=\mu(n)$,那么$F(n)=\varphi(n)$,和</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">a_{k}(m)=\sum_{d \mid(m, k)}\mu(d)=\left\{\begin{array}{lll}1 & \text{若} & (m,k)=1 \\0 & \text{若} & (m,k)>1\end{array}\right.</script><p>由上面的结论就能得到.</p><p><strong>注</strong> 命题(1)亦可由简单的Mobius反演导出:</p></blockquote><p>考虑所有$n$次单位根的$k$次方和$\eta_n(k)$,那么</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\eta_n(k)=\sum_{i=1}^n \xi_n^{ik}=\sum_{d\mid n}c_d(k)</script><p>由Mobius反演可得</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">c_n(k)=\sum_{d\mid n}\mu(n/d)\eta_d(k)</script><p>由于</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\eta_{q}(n)=\begin{cases}0 &, q \nmid n \\ q &, q \mid n\end{cases}</script><p>这就得到</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">c_n(k)=\sum_{d\mid(k,n)}d\mu\left(\frac{n}{d}\right)</script>]]></content>
      
      
